      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768794052540,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Staffs and doctor spend all the time on the screen still sometime they never understand the dashboard.\n- Time consuming\n- Lack of context\n- scattered system all dashboard running standalone require different onboarding.\n- data never talk to each other dashboard increasing extra 10-20 minutes per task . ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Staffs and doctor spend all the time on the screen still sometime they never understand the dashboard.\n- Time consuming\n- Lack of context\n- scattered system all dashboard running standalone require different onboarding.\n- data never talk to each other dashboard increasing extra 10-20 minutes per task . ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
